WEBVTT

00:05.089 --> 00:08.119
(male narrator)
Long, long ago,
deep in the forest

00:08.140 --> 00:12.089
there was a hidden village
where tiny creatures lived.

00:12.109 --> 00:15.019
They call themselves Smurfs.

00:15.039 --> 00:16.230
They were good.

00:17.010 --> 00:19.140
[theme music]

00:22.120 --> 00:26.129
Then there was Gargamel,
the evil wizard.

00:26.149 --> 00:27.219
He was bad.

00:28.000 --> 00:30.050
Oh, I hate Smurfs.

00:31.140 --> 00:34.020
I'll get you,
I'll get all of you

00:34.039 --> 00:36.159
if it's the last thing
I ever do!

00:36.179 --> 00:38.140
[evil laughter]

00:38.159 --> 00:39.149
Unh!

00:39.170 --> 00:41.100
Oh, I'll get you.

00:41.119 --> 00:44.140
I'll find your village someday.
You'll be sorry!

00:44.159 --> 00:47.030
(male narrator)
Well, the forest
is still there

00:47.049 --> 00:51.070
and if you listen,
you may hear Gargamel's rage.

00:51.090 --> 00:53.200
And if you are good,
you may just

00:53.219 --> 00:56.200
catch a glimpse
of the Smurfs.

